.TH CONV-WARDEN 1 "July 2026" "ConVigurator Manual"
.SH NAME
conv-warden \- links SSH configurations to the Goldwarden / Bitwarden agent.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B conv-warden
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B conv-warden
updates terminal configuration profiles (.bashrc, .zshrc, config.fish) and ~/.ssh/config to point the SSH_AUTH_SOCK to ~/.goldwarden-ssh-agent.sock.
This enables automatic SSH authentication and git signing using credentials stored in your Bitwarden vault.
.SH SEE ALSO
conv-shell(1), ssh(1)
